<title>USA: SWVA Bancshares to buy back shares.</title>
<headline>SWVA Bancshares to buy back shares.</headline>
<dateline>ROANOKE, Va. 1997-04-18</dateline>
<text>
<p>SWVA Bancshares Inc said Thursday it has received regulatory approval to buy back up to five percent of its stock.</p>
<p>Five percent of its stock would be 26,021 shares, the company said.</p>
<p>The repurchases are expected to be made in the open market. The repurchased shares are to become authorized but unissued shares, and will be used for general corporate purposes, including the issuance of shares related to the exercise of stock options.</p>
<p>The buy back program is expected to be completed by October 7.</p>
